latestIgtvVideos.title: Testing the Primark liquid shadow duo
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
🚨 Review alert 🚨 So I tested the @primark liquid shadow duo.

I created a very subtle everyday look. 
So for starters, it’s a good dupe for the Huda beauty melted shadows.

The pros ✅ 1. It is really easy to use 2. Blends very easily 3. It can be built up 4. Very inexpensive 
The cons ❌ 1. Not as pigmented as I’d hope... BUT for a product that doesn’t cost much I think it is well worth your money!
